snippet.title: Hapunan - Official Trailer | A Filipino Horror Story Game
snippet.description:
Hapunan is a story-driven horror game inspired by Filipino culture. I made this using Unity Game Engine.

🎮 Add it to your itch.io collection now: https://yikon.itch.io/hapunan
